'''''Kaddu Beykat''''' ( Letter from My Village cyagwa ''Lettre paysanne'' ) ni filime yo [[Senegali|muri Senegal yo mu]] 1975 iyobowe na Safi Faye<ref>Kaddu Beykat | Activities | CCCB <nowiki>https://www.cccb.org</nowiki> › activities › file › kaddu-beykat</ref> . Niyo filime ya mbere yerekanwe yakozwe n’umugore wo muri Afurika yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara yatanzwe mu bucuruzi kandi izana amahanga ku muyobozi wayo. <ref name="NFU">Ukadike, p.30</ref> <ref name="LS">Spaas, p.185</ref> Ishingiye ku rukundo, ivuga ubuzima bwa buri munsi bw'abantu bo mucyaro cya Senegal<ref>Letter from My Village / Kaddu Beykat | African Film Festival, Inc. <nowiki>https://africanfilmny.org</nowiki> › films › letter-from-my-villag...</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Ngor ni umusore uba mu mudugudu wa Senegali wifuza kurongora Coumba. amapfa yo mu mudugudu afite ingaruka kubihingwa<ref>Letter From My Village (Kaddu Beykat) - SPLA Pro <nowiki>http://www.spla.pro</nowiki> › file.film.letter-from-my-village-k...</ref>, nuko Ngor ntashobore kubona  inkwano ya Columba<ref>Kaddu beykat (1976) – rarefilmm | The Cave of Forgotten Films <nowiki>http://rarefilmm.com</nowiki> › 2020/11 › kaddu-beykat-1976</ref>. Yagiye mu murwa mukuru wa Senegali, Dakar, kugira ngo agerageze gushaka amafaranga menshi<ref>Safi Faye - Black Women Directors <nowiki>https://www.blackwomendirectors.co</nowiki> › safi-faye</ref> . Agaruka ku baturage maze abwira abandi ibyamubayeho mu mujyi<ref>Letter from My Village (1976) | MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › letter-from-my-village</ref>. Iyi nkuru yerekana ubuzima bwa buri munsi bw'abaturage, ivuga uburyo bw'ibaruwa yandikiye inshuti ye, izwi nka Faye. <ref name="SR">Russell, p. 59</ref>

